sense.def:
A jumble
je veliko različnih stvari, ki so zmedeno in neurejeno pomešane skupaj.

seg.quote: ...a chaotic jumble of motor vehicles of every description.

sense.def:
To jumble things
ali
to jumble things up
pomeni stvari premešati, da niso v pravem redu.

seg.quote: The bits and pieces were jumbled up with a lot of stuff that would never be needed again.
